txt.en: These supplies were ruined during the fall

'I see, some of the crates broke during the fall. Hopefully, if I sort through what you did manage to recover, I will soon enough find my tools and supplies. Treasure hunting awaits after all! Thank you, [placeholder]!'
Dargumë can be found at Asbaj-khîrfin.\n\nYou should bring the supplies to Dargumë.
Supplies can be found in northern Máttugard.\n\nYou should recover supplies.

'I ventured out here in Máttugard to hunt for treasure. It is a passion of mine, you see. I would already be out there hunting for it if it were not for the fact that I am still awaiting my tools and supplies. There was a supply cart travelling behind us. The supply cart met an unfortunate accident and all that it carried, including my tools and supplies, tumbled out and fell a great distance!\n\n'If you are able, would you locate the fallen supplies for me? I would be most grateful to be reunited with the tools I need to hunt for treasure!'
An accident involving a supply cart has left the dwarves' supplies strewn about Máttugard.
